name: Tunnel Rush (itch) (Breaking_Reality)
description:
Tunnel Rush! 
Rush through an infinitely generated tunnel while dodging obstacles that increase in difficulty over time! Can you rush to get that high-score?!

This game is based on the original Tunnel Rush. My version of tunnel rush is very basic compared to this version, I would consider it a draft or concept game. There is so much more that can be done gameplay wise!
